'''Borstel Galactic Defense''',<ref name="Knights of Fate" /> also known simply as '''Borstel''',<ref name="RVG" /> was a company who produced the [[NNJ-40 "Thunderbolt" long-range ion cannon]] used on [[RX-200 Falchion-class assault tank|RX-200 ''Falchion''-class assault tanks]] of the [[Galactic Republic]]<ref name="Knights of Fate" /> and also produced the [[NK-7 ion cannon]]s used in the armaments of the [[Galactic Empire]]'s [[Imperial I-class Star Destroyer|''Imperial I-class'' Star Destroyers]].<ref name="RVG" /> They also made the [[RG-9 laser cannon]]s on the [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor]].<ref name="FlightLog" />

